[{"url_token": "upzeng", "headline": "智能穿戴", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4588941219", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "4588941219", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我们家也是太阳能和燃气热水器同时供热水，每次用燃气热水器必须把太阳能热水器的阀门关掉（太阳能上下水共用一根管），用太阳能热水器必须把燃气进水阀关上。两个阀门不能同时开，否则，会串水到太阳能水箱，导致太阳能热水器水满后，水从太阳能溢水孔流出，请教如何解决太阳能阀不关闭的情况下，用燃气热水器时不出现串水？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "upzeng", "author_id": "cff2532a924d8bf93218a0cfc6380233", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "hen-lan-de-qin-kuai-ren", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "3029566029", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "水是怎样改的呢？是不是太阳能，燃气炉的热水管都要留一个总开关阀，", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "风筝", "author_id": "51d10b0ec92c28ce01f5f27d2365b712", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "hen-lan-de-qin-kuai-ren", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4466475071", "reply_comment_id": "4439033645", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "好，谢谢哈", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "风筝", "author_id": "51d10b0ec92c28ce01f5f27d2365b712", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hen-lan-de-qin-kuai-ren", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4466055454", "reply_comment_id": "4439033645", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "好，谢谢哈", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "风筝", "author_id": "51d10b0ec92c28ce01f5f27d2365b712", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shi-chu-xin-yi", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4439033645", "reply_comment_id": "4436507817", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我装修在十多年前，当时找的改水师傅，他依据我的想法琢磨着做的水路。<br>热水以太阳能为主，燃气热水器为辅。当时也没想到给太阳能装开关阀。<br>装了个混水阀混合太阳能的热水和自来水。混水阀的出水管路和燃气热水器的出水管路连接。<br>感觉燃气热水器出水的压力大于太阳能的。想用燃气热水器，打开燃气热水器角阀和开关j就行，这样管路里流着的就是燃气热水器的水。<br>现在，燃气热水器升级换代，有可能有更好的改造方法，我家的仅供参考哈", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "时出新意", "author_id": "df35fae1e1b0f0360eb99224415ce571", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hen-lan-de-qin-kuai-ren", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4436507817", "reply_comment_id": "4401254304", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "太阳能那边两个角阀，燃气炉那边两个角阀，用哪个开那个，对吧？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "风筝", "author_id": "51d10b0ec92c28ce01f5f27d2365b712", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shi-chu-xin-yi", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4401254304", "reply_comment_id": "3029566029", "reply_root_comment_id": "3029566029", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "太阳能和燃气没有总开关。<br>使用太阳能热水时，燃气的冷热水角阀处在关闭状态就行。<br>想用燃气热水，打开角阀即可。<br>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "时出新意", "author_id": "df35fae1e1b0f0360eb99224415ce571", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}]